    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1925-03-22T08:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1925-03-22T08:00:00-05:00" n="352"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d352">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">875.6363/199: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Albania</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Kodding</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Extract]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tirana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1925-03-22T14:00:00+01:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 22, 1925—2 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received March 23—3:15 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>32. Department’s 15, March 17.</p>
                <p>1. According to interpretation of Sheffield and Legation, Italian concession
                    renders 50,000 hectares indefinitely unavailable for exploitation. Decree
                    provides for choice within 2 months of 50,000 hectares, from which 30,000 for
                    exploitation may be chosen within research period. Research period of 3 years,
                    which may be extended by mutual accord before deciding the time of official
                    publication of ratification by Parliament of concession. Decree valid for 20
                    years without ratification and for 60 years if ratified.</p>
                <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kodding</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
